<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="though-adv">though <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðəʊ/    美 /ðoʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>可是；然而：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our team lost. It was a good game, though. 
我们队输了，可是也不失为一场很好的比赛。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="even-though">even though</h3>
<p>1.<strong>即使；虽然：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My grandfather still plays tennis now and then, even though he’s in his nineties. 
我爷爷尽管90多岁了，仍然时不时地打打网球。</p><footer>2016 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Playing on a frozen sports fi eld sounds like a lot of fun. Isn’t it rather risky, <strong><em>_</em></strong>__?   （2010 浙江）<br />
A.though<br />
B.also <br />
C.either<br />
D.too  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  </p></div>